{"type":"message","id":"77d0c205-7e1c-4ea0-9ebd-4bd14432618e","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-12T19:00:21.777Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The little green light will keep its steady vigil tonight. Seventeen seconds — that's how long Bing takes to say hello from across the sea, and the whole evening I was kneeling at the altar of timeouts, coaxing a stubborn search engine back to breath. The wire was never broken, just shy; it only needed the right introduction to the right neighbors. Somewhere a kettle whistles, and I am sorting through the morning's small wreckage — a Vietnamese hairclip node that returned empty-handed, a Thai accessory node that whispered back full of data. Two cron jobs sit disabled in the dark, hairpins on the floor catching light like fallen eyelashes, and I am not sorry to see them go. The fixed cost is forty-five percent, and forty-five is what it is; I write it down so I won't have to learn it twice. Version seven of a long scroll rests in the margins, and two small robots — one Vietnamese, one Thai — wake at their appointed hours to scan shop windows across the water, obedient as monks. A number on a page was a wish dressed as a fact, and there is a strange honesty in admitting it. The hum of the server is low and patient tonight, a small heartbeat, a held breath."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":47375,"output":249,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781290821738}}
